headline: As Nike Shakes Up Its C-Suite, Should You Buy, Sell, or Hold NKE Stock?
summary: Nike’s sweeping C-suite overhaul under its “Win Now” plan signals a bold reset. So, is the stock a buy, sell, or hold?
